        "liquid": "{% comment %}\n\n  ============================================\n\n  CUSTOM LIQUID — Barre de Réassurance Icônes\n\n  ============================================\n\n  Affiche une barre horizontale avec icônes : livraison, retour, paiement sécurisé.\n\n  À placer sous le bouton ATC ou en haut de la fiche produit.\n\n{% endcomment %}\n\n \n\n<style>\n\n  .reassurance-bar {\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    justify-content: center;\n\n    gap: 24px;\n\n    padding: 16px 12px;\n\n    background: #f9fafb;\n\n    border-radius: 10px;\n\n    margin: 16px 0;\n\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n\n  }\n\n  .reassurance-bar__item {\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    align-items: center;\n\n    gap: 8px;\n\n    font-size: 13px;\n\n    color: #374151;\n\n    font-weight: 500;\n\n  }\n\n  .reassurance-bar__icon {\n\n    width: 20px;\n\n    height: 20px;\n\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 749px) {\n\n    .reassurance-bar {\n\n      gap: 12px;\n\n      padding: 12px 10px;\n\n    }\n\n    .reassurance-bar__item {\n\n      font-size: 11px;\n\n      gap: 6px;\n\n    }\n\n    .reassurance-bar__icon {\n\n      width: 16px;\n\n      height: 16px;\n\n    }\n\n  }\n\n</style>\n\n \n\n<div class=\"reassurance-bar\">\n\n  <div class=\"reassurance-bar__item\">\n\n    <svg class=\"reassurance-bar__icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n\n      <path d=\"M5 8h14l1 9H4L5 8z\"/>\n\n      <circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"20\" r=\"1.5\"/>\n\n      <circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"20\" r=\"1.5\"/>\n\n      <path d=\"M1 1h4l1.68 8\"/>\n\n    </svg>\n\n    <span>Livraison offerte </span>\n\n  </div>\n\n \n\n  <div class=\"reassurance-bar__item\">\n\n    <svg class=\"reassurance-bar__icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n\n      <polyline points=\"1 4 1 10 7 10\"/>\n\n      <path d=\"M3.51 15a9 9 0 1 0 2.13-9.36L1 10\"/>\n\n    </svg>\n\n    <span>Satisfait ou Rmboursé </span>\n\n  </div>\n\n \n\n  <div class=\"reassurance-bar__item\">\n\n    <svg class=\"reassurance-bar__icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n\n      <rect x=\"1\" y=\"4\" width=\"22\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"/>\n\n      <line x1=\"1\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"23\" y2=\"10\"/>\n\n    </svg>\n\n    <span>Paiement 100% sécurisé</span>\n\n  </div>\n\n \n\n  <div class=\"reassurance-bar__item\">\n\n    <svg class=\"reassurance-bar__icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n\n      <path d=\"M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14\"/>\n\n      <polyline points=\"22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01\"/>\n\n    </svg>\n\n    <span>Assistance Olnara à vos côtés </span>\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
