    "custom_liquid_M6acyA": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "{% comment %}\n  ============================================\n  CUSTOM LIQUID — Avis Vedette Style Olnara\n  ============================================\n{% endcomment %}\n\n<style>\n  .featured-review {\n    position: relative;\n    padding: 32px 24px;\n    background-color: #272759; /* Ton bleu profond */\n    border-radius: 16px;\n    margin: 24px 0;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .featured-review__quote {\n    font-size: 64px;\n    color: #FFFFFF; \n    opacity: 0.15; /* Très léger pour le style */\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 8px;\n    left: 20px;\n    font-family: Georgia, serif;\n    line-height: 1;\n  }\n  \n  .featured-review__title {\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #F0F0F0; /* Texte clair */\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n    position: relative;\n    z-index: 1;\n  }\n\n  .featured-review__stars {\n    color: #f59e0b; /* Jaune ambre pour les étoiles */\n    font-size: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: 3px;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n  }\n  .featured-review__text {\n    font-size: 18px;\n    color: #F0F0F0; /* Texte clair */\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    font-style: italic;\n    max-width: 560px;\n    margin: 0 auto 16px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n  }\n  .featured-review__author {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .featured-review__name {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #F0F0F0; /* Texte clair */\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n  .featured-review__verified {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    color: #F0F0F0; /* Texte clair comme demandé */\n    font-weight: 600;\n    opacity: 0.8; /* Légèrement transparent pour différencier du nom */\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 749px) {\n    .featured-review { padding: 24px 16px; }\n    .featured-review__title { font-size: 18px; }\n    .featured-review__text { font-size: 15px; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"featured-review\">\n  <span class=\"featured-review__quote\">\"</span>\n  \n  <div class=\"featured-review__title\">Recommandé par les professionnels de santé !</div>\n  \n \n\n  <p class=\"featured-review__text\">\n    <br>Je vois trop souvent des lésions dues à un nettoyage à l'aveugle. \n    <br><strong>Le Nettoyeur Olnara</strong> change la donne : la caméra HD permet enfin un retrait précis du cérumen sans risque pour le tympan. \n    <br>C'est l'outil d'hygiène préventive que je recommande pour toute la famille.\n  </p>\n  \n  <div class=\"featured-review__author\">\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"featured-review__name\">Dr. John Harris</div>\n      <div class=\"featured-review__verified\">Audiologiste certifié</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "background": "",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": ""
      }
    },
    "custom_liquid_4z7Ma6": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": false,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "{% comment %}\n\n  ============================================\n\n  CUSTOM LIQUID — Carrousel Avis Clients Photos\n\n  ============================================\n\n  Carrousel horizontal d'avis avec avatar et étoiles.\n\n  Défilement tactile sur mobile.\n\n{% endcomment %}\n\n \n\n<style>\n\n  .reviews-carousel {\n\n    padding: 24px 0;\n\n    margin: 20px 0;\n\n  }\n\n  .reviews-carousel__title {\n\n    font-size: 20px;\n\n    font-weight: 700;\n\n    text-align: center;\n\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n\n    color: #111827;\n\n  }\n\n  .reviews-carousel__track {\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    gap: 16px;\n\n    overflow-x: auto;\n\n    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n\n    padding: 4px 16px 16px;\n\n    scrollbar-width: none;\n\n  }\n\n  .reviews-carousel__track::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n\n  .review-card {\n\n    min-width: 280px;\n\n    max-width: 300px;\n\n    background: #fff;\n\n    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\n\n    border-radius: 12px;\n\n    padding: 20px;\n\n    scroll-snap-align: start;\n\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n\n    transition: transform 0.2s;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }\n\n  .review-card__header {\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    align-items: center;\n\n    gap: 10px;\n\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__avatar {\n\n    width: 40px;\n\n    height: 40px;\n\n    border-radius: 50%;\n\n    background: #eff6ff;\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    align-items: center;\n\n    justify-content: center;\n\n    font-weight: 700;\n\n    color: #3b82f6;\n\n    font-size: 16px;\n\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__name {\n\n    font-weight: 600;\n\n    font-size: 14px;\n\n    color: #111827;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__badge {\n\n    font-size: 10px;\n\n    color: #10b981;\n\n    font-weight: 600;\n\n    display: flex;\n\n    align-items: center;\n\n    gap: 3px;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__stars {\n\n    color: #f59e0b;\n\n    font-size: 14px;\n\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__text {\n\n    font-size: 13px;\n\n    color: #4b5563;\n\n    line-height: 1.6;\n\n  }\n\n  .review-card__date {\n\n    font-size: 11px;\n\n    color: #9ca3af;\n\n    margin-top: 10px;\n\n  }\n\n</style>\n\n \n\n<div id = \"avis\" class=\"reviews-carousel\">\n\n  <h3 class=\"reviews-carousel__title\">Ce que nos clients disent</h3>\n\n  <div class=\"reviews-carousel__track\">\n\n <div class=\"review-card\">\n  <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n    <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">I</div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__name\">Inès B.</div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★★</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__text\">Franchement bluffant. On voit super bien sur le téléphone, c’est même un peu addictif de regarder lol. L'embout est très doux.</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 3 jours</div>\n</div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n\n        <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">M</div>\n\n        <div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__name\">Marie L.</div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★★</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__text\">Produit de qualité exceptionnelle ! L'emballage était soigné et la livraison ultra rapide. Je recommande à 100%.</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 3 jours</div>\n\n    </div>\n\n \n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n\n        <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">T</div>\n\n        <div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__name\">Thomas B.</div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★★</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__text\">Deuxième commande ici et toujours aussi satisfait. Le service client est top, ils m'ont répondu en 1h.</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 1 semaine</div>\n\n    </div>\n\n\n\n <div class=\"review-card\">\n  <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n    <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">S</div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__name\">Samir K.</div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__text\">Produit de qualité et conforme. La connexion wifi avec l'appli demande un petit temps d'adaptation au début mais après ça marche nickel.</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 1 semaine</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n\n        <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">S</div>\n\n        <div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__name\">Sophie R.</div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__text\">Très bon rapport qualité-prix. Le produit correspond parfaitement à la description. Petit bémol sur le délai, sinon parfait.</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 2 semaines</div>\n\n    </div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"review-card\">\n  <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n    <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">C</div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__name\">Chloé V.</div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★☆☆</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__text\">Le nettoyeur est bien mais j'ai reçu le carton un peu écrasé... Heureusement l'appareil n'avait rien. Fonctionne bien.</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 2 semaines</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n <div class=\"review-card\">\n  <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n    <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">S</div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__name\">Sarah J.</div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★★</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__text\">enfin un truc qui marche et qui fait pas mal !! la boite est tres jolie en plus. je recommande sans hesiter merci olnara</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 5 jours</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"review-card\">\n  <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n    <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">L</div>\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__name\">Lucas P.</div>\n      <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__text\">Bien reçu mon Pure Cleaner. La camera est très claire. J'aurais aimé une batterie qui dure un peu plus longtemps mais ça suffit largement pour une séance.</div>\n  <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 1 mois</div>\n</div>\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__header\">\n\n        <div class=\"review-card__avatar\">J</div>\n\n        <div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__name\">Julien D.</div>\n\n          <div class=\"review-card__badge\">✓ Achat vérifié</div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__stars\">★★★★★</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__text\">J'ai offert ce produit à ma femme, elle était ravie. La qualité est vraiment au rendez-vous. Bravo !</div>\n\n      <div class=\"review-card__date\">Il y a 3 semaines</div>\n\n    </div>\n\n \n\n  </div>\n\n</div>",
        "background": "",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": ""
      }
    }
  },
